Authentication Flow (Flowchart)
flowchart TD
    A[User enters password] --> B[Hash password]
    B --> C[Compare with stored hash]
    C -->|Match| D[Login Successful]
    C -->|No Match| E[Access Denied]

->  Password Hashing Diagram
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant DB

    User->>App: Enter Password
    App->>App: Hash + Salt
    App->>DB: Compare Hash
    DB-->>App: Match / No Match

-> Practical Implementation (Python)
hash_password.py
import hashlib

password = "Cyber@123"
hashed = hashlib.sha256(password.encode()).hexdigest()

print("Original Password:", password)
print("Hashed Password:", hashed)
